name: Doge Pup
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en: DOGEPUP is a deflationary cryptocurrency featuring a maximum supply of 50,000 tokens. The DOGEPUP token is a yield farming token based on the Dogechain. A utility vault dAPP is being developed alongside the yield farm creating revenue to buyback and burn DOGEPUP tokens.
